data.title: State & Alternative Fuel Provider Fleets: Metropolitan Statistical Areas Covered by EPAct
data.text:
Metropolitan Statistical Areas Covered by EPAct

The U.S. Department of Energy has defined covered Metropolitan Statistical Areas/Consolidated Metropolitan Statistical Areas (MSA/CMSA) by the 1980 U.S. Census population figures and by the 1990 U.S. Census MSA/CMSA area definitions. Cities are listed for partially covered counties only. If no cities are shown, the entire county is covered.
